tgs:Concept.CircleOfTrustLocalism thinkr:echoesIdeaOf tgs:Persona.ElinorOstrom .

tgs:Concept.ComplexityCollapse thinkr:influencedBy tgs:Persona.JosephTainter .

tgs:Concept.DiscountRatesAndPresentBias thinkr:echoesIdeaOf tgs:Persona.MarcusAurelius .

tgs:Concept.EnergyBlindness thinkr:contrastsWith tgs:Persona.Buddha .

tgs:Concept.JevonsParadox thinkr:influencedBy tgs:Persona.WilliamStanleyJevons .

tgs:Concept.Metacrisis thinkr:influencedBy tgs:Persona.GregoryBateson .

tgs:Concept.MoneyAsClaimOnEnergy thinkr:echoesIdeaOf tgs:Persona.Aristotle .

tgs:Concept.PeakOil thinkr:influencedBy tgs:Persona.MKingHubbert .

tgs:Concept.Superorganism thinkr:influencedBy tgs:Persona.EOWilson .

tgs:Concept.Wetware thinkr:echoesIdeaOf tgs:Persona.SigmundFreud .

tgs:Persona.MartinLutherKingJr thinkr:appliesTo tgs:Concept.GrowthImperative .

tgs:Concept.LimitsToGrowth thinkr:influencedBy tgs:Persona.DennisMeadows,
        tgs:Persona.DonellaMeadows .

tgs:SchoolOfThought.DoughnutEconomics thinkr:convergesWith tgs:Concept.Overshoot .

tgs:Concept.Overshoot thinkr:convergesWith tgs:SchoolOfThought.DoughnutEconomics ;
    thinkr:influencedBy tgs:Persona.WilliamCatton .

thinkr:LinkNote a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:comment "Metadata resource attached to a single cross-link triple (rationale, confidence). See data/seed/links.ttl for the pattern. Migrate to RDF-star once you're comfortable — Oxigraph supports it — to attach this directly to the triple instead of via a side resource."@en ;
    skos:prefLabel "Link Note"@en .

